modelVersions.name: Sinon GGO v1
modelVersions.description:
Sinon (GGO Version)

Works best at 0.6-0.9 or above.

Trained with AbyssOrangeMixv2 but does fairly well with most other models. Can do NSFW, you may have to prompt aggressive (or use a lower weight)

First time uploading, It's not a perfect model and I'm not an expert but I am also not as picky.
